snippet.title: Skeleton Boomerang - Trailer
snippet.description: Coming soon from ANIM.ACE is a new skeletastic action sidescroller. In Skeletoon Boomerang, you explore an island to search for an evil voodoo lord so you can stop his army of skeletons, and free yourself from an evil curse. Use your boomerang powers to defeat enemies and rack up huge combos, while going through a variety of exciting environments and challenging bosses.
